          "value": "<p>When a junk golem begins its turn with half its HP or fewer, it must attempt a DC 11 Will save. On a failure, it goes berserk, using its actions to move and attack or make a full attack. If it can’t reach a creature, it attacks objects. The golem attempts a DC 11 Will saving throw at the end of each of its turns to end the berserk state. If the golem’s creator communicates with it to calm it and succeeds at a DC 10 Charisma check, the golem gains a +2 circumstance bonus to this save.</p>"
